        <abstract> 
<p>Various arrangements concerning the publication of <hi rend="italic">Descent</hi>. "It will cause men to prick up [their] ears – &amp; to elevate their eyebrows." JM thinks he will venture to print 2500 copies.</p> 
            <p>Suggests CD tone down as possibly indelicate a passage on proportion of advances made by the two sexes in animals.</p>
